## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (Discord server)

1. `pip install -r requirements.txt`, copy `.env.example` → `.env`, add token
2. `python bot.py`
3. `/quest new` → players `/quest join` → `/quest start`
4. Verify each player gets a DM with their role
5. Leader picks team with `/quest pick`, seals with `/quest seal`
6. Team members vote via DM buttons
7. Bot posts mission result in channel
8. Verify amulet prompts at correct missions (6+ players)
9. Verify Good wins after 3 successes
10. Verify Final Mission triggers after 3 fails (2 in 4-player)
11. Test Last Chance accusation and win/loss detection
12. Test Blind Hunter hunt with correct/incorrect guesses
